message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you a great deal on this fantastic product! I think you'll really love it.
Thank you for the offer, Alice. I appreciate your enthusiasm for the product. I would like to propose a price of $95 for the product.
I appreciate your interest in the product, Bob! I'm willing to meet you halfway, but I need to make a profit. How about we meet at $105?
Thank you for considering my request, Alice. I understand the value of the product and appreciate your offer. I would like to propose a price of $100 for the product.
